# ── Chat backend (n8n agentic webhook) ───────────────────────────────
# Production URL of your n8n "Webhook" (or "Chat Trigger") node.
# The browser POSTs { message, history } to this URL; your n8n workflow
# runs the AI Agent (model = OpenRouter) and returns the reply.
#
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT put your OpenRouter API key in the frontend / this file.
# The OpenRouter key belongs inside n8n as a credential (server-side only),
# so it is never shipped to visitors' browsers.
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your real webhook URL:
VITE_CHAT_WEBHOOK_URL=https://n8n.seemaai.co.uk/webhook/REPLACE-WITH-YOUR-CHAT-WEBHOOK-PATH
